The file contained in this folder called database?builder.py is a python file that builds a database of PhysCell simulations varying the values of their metabolic parameters according to SOBOL sequences.
The user has to specify the value of different variables before executing the file>
  1. Number of parameters to vary//line 627
  2. Number of simulations of the database// line 630
  3. Path of the PhysiCell folder//line 624
  4. Number of simulations with each parameter combination//line762
  5. Range of each parameter//lines 646 to 665
In addition to that, all the parameters to be optimized have to be set to 0.0 in their demo.xml beofre the start of the simulation.
The results are created in the PhysiCell folder in a series of txt files.
